<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome to Echelon</title>
    <style>
        body,
        html {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: #eee;
        }

        .content {
            max-width: 400px;
            height: auto;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: .3em;
            line-height: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            padding: 10px;
            background: #eee;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .regards,
        a {
            color: #D4A5A5;
        }

        .warning {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeeba;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #856404;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="content">
            <header class="header">
                <img src="https://www.echelonsclub.com/logo.jpg" alt="Logo" width="80">
            </header>
            <section>
                <p>Hello, {{username}}</p>
                <small>
                    Thank you for joining us. We are thrilled to have you as part of our exclusive community.

                    At Echelon, our goal is to provide you with an unforgettable experience where trust, exploration,
                    and
                    pleasure come together. Should you have any questions or need guidance, our team is here to support
                    you confidentially and respectfully.
                </small>
                <br /><br />
                <small><a href="{{link}}">Login</a> to access your account and begin your journey.</small>

                <div class="warning">
                    <strong>Important Notice:</strong><br />
                    For your safety, <strong>do not make any payments offline</strong>, including to any DOM. Numerous
                    scams have
                    been reported. If someone requests offline payment, please contact our official support team
                    immediately.<br />
                    <br />
                    We accept a variety of secure payment methods: <strong>PayPal, Apple Pay, Cash App, Gift Cards,
                        Crypto,
                        Venmo, Zelle,</strong> and <strong>Chime</strong>.
                </div>

                <p class="regards"><b>Echelon's Team</b></p>
                <center style="font-size: 10px; color: gray;">Copyright &copy; Echelon's Club. All rights reserved.
                </center>
            </section>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>